  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Scope :</p><ul><li><p>Efficiently organizing schedules, handling incoming and outgoing correspondence, and maintaining organized files both digitally and physically.</p></li><li><p>Assessing and prioritizing tasks to maximize productivity, coordinating with team members to ensure timely completion of assignments.</p></li><li><p>Scheduling meetings, booking venues, and preparing necessary materials such as agendas, presentations, and reports.</p></li><li><p>Serving as a point of contact for internal and external stakeholders, promptly responding to calls, emails, and inquiries, and facilitating smooth communication channels.</p></li><li><p>Managing expense reports, tracking expenditures, and handling personal finances as required.</p></li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li><p>Admin or assistant experience is a plus</p></li><li><p>Having a driver's license is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Bachelor's degree or equivalent experience.</p></li><li><p>Strong organizational and good communication skills.</p></li><li><p>Discretion, adaptability, and multitasking ability.</p></li></ul><p>Aurora Asia Pacific (21C0671)|Stephanie (R21100585)</p>",
